OL,4,CGive workers full rights from day one -
OL,5,CLabour
OL,6, Workers should be given "full"
OL,7, employment rights from day one, Labour
OL,8, has said as it announces plans to
OL,9, "fundamentally change the economy".
OL,11,FCurrently some rights - such as being
OL,12,Fable to request flexible working - only
OL,13,Fkick in at a later stage.
OL,15,FLabour is also calling for a ban on
OL,16,F"fire and re-hire" practices.
OL,18,FMinister Amanda Milling said the
OL,19,Fgovernment had provided "unprecedented"
OL,20,Fsupport to workers during the pandemic
OL,21,Fthrough the furlough scheme.
